---
description: Melodia UI branding and visual consistency—use when editing pages, components, global styles, Tailwind theme, or design-system tokens (colors, typography, motion, shared primitives).
globs: src/app/**/*.tsx, src/components/**/*.tsx, src/**/*.css, tailwind.config.*, src/lib/design-system.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

Before changing visuals, layout, or component styling:

- Read @joyful-jam-session-brand-kit.md for brand colors, tone, and visual guidelines.
- Use @src/lib/design-system.ts for shared tokens, transitions, and UI building blocks.
- Use CSS variables from @src/app/globals.css (colors, spacing, typography) to stay consistent with the theme.

Prefer patterns already established in those files rather than one-off styling.
